ylaw.org.uk/ Holy Law Hebrew South Broughton Congregation], Prestwich<ref name="Holy Law">{{Cite web |url=https://www.jewishgen.org/jcr-uk/Community/m21_holy/index.htm |title=Holy Law South Broughton Congregation |date=1 January 2018 |publisher=JCR-UK |access-date=27 October 2018}}</ref> * Kehilas Kol Yaakov, Prestwich<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.federation.org.uk/communities/kehillas-kol-yaakov/ |title=Kehillas Kol Yaakov |website=Federation |access-date=25 September 2018}}</ref><ref name="KKY">{{Cite web |url=https://www.jewishgen.org/jcr-uk/Community/m13_damesek/index.htm |title=Damesek Eliezer Synagogue (Prestwich Beth Hamedrash) |date=29 June 2017 |publisher=JCR-UK |access-date=25 September 2018}}</ref> *[[King David School, Manchester|King David High School, Manchester]] [http://www.kdhs.org.uk/] *[http://www.lchaim.org.uk/templates/articlecco_cdo/aid/962544/jewish/About-Us.htm L'chaim Chabad-Lubavitch], Salford *[http://www.mljc.org.uk Manchester Liberal Jewish Community] *[[Manchester Reform Synagogue]] (Jackson's Row) [http://www.jacksonsrow.org/] *[http://www.meadehillshul.co.uk/ Meade Hill Shul], Prestwich *[[Menorah Synagogue |Menorah Synagogue: Cheshire Reform Congregation]], Manchester [http://www.menorah.org.uk/] *[http://ohryerushalayim.org.uk/ Ohr Yerushalayim], Salford * Sedgley Park Synagogue (Shomrei Hadass), Prestwich<ref name="Shomrei Hadass">{{Cite web |url=https://www.google.com/search?q=Sedgley+Park+Synagogue+%28Shomrei+Hadass%29&ie=utf-8&oe=utf-8&client=firefox-b-ab |title=Sedgley Park Synagogue (Shomrei Hadass) |date=26 February 2017 |publisher=JCR-UK |access-date=25 September 2018}}</ref> *[[Sha'arei Shalom]] [http://www.shaareishalommanchester.org.uk/], Whitefield *[[South Manchester Synagogue]] [http://www.southmanchestersynagogue.org.uk/] [[Bowdon, Greater Manchester|Bowdon]] *Talmud Torah Chinuch N'orim Synagogue, Salford<ref name="Talmud Salford">{{Cite web |url=https://www.jewishgen.org/jcr-uk/Community/m38_tt-chinuch/index.htm 